_:Nc3975aeb3bd644e29a1d84341d83ce9c <http://schema.org/description> "UK Visas and Immigration (UKVI) is responsible for making millions of decisions every year about who has the right to visit or stay in the country, with a firm emphasis on national security and a culture of customer satisfaction for people who come here legally. UKVI is part of the Home Office ." .
